{"tid":2208101,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"人類如何在一場跑步比賽上快過光到達終點？","createTime":"2020-09-18T15:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T05:03:16.000Z","uid":51346,"like":64,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"90b050b0d0c5b848abc6c861e464d731cc77de8a","tid":2208101,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9T6Vpfy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9T6Vpfy.jpg&h=983d2145&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先要預備一支電筒代表光 同時放塊鏡喺終點 <br />\n開始比賽後 只要鏡出現電筒射出嚟嘅光 就代表光贏（唔計折射）<br />\n人類就衝線當贏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後我哋加個欄喺中間 等呢場比賽變成一個跨欄比賽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XvxJyai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXvxJyai.jpg&h=c3bcf46e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比賽開始<br />\n開電筒 啲光畀個欄擋晒<br />\n人類檻過個欄 慢慢行向終點 輕鬆獲勝"},{"pid":"760011e50cf0c19802f59ae14ad7591d61ef0638","tid":2208101,"uid":51346,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:28:39.000Z","msg":"可以周圍同人講我快過光了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf5dc974cd35557844fe84cad111165089f19bc","tid":2208101,"uid":312333,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:28:54.000Z","msg":"巴打，我留意咗你好耐，你真係好幽默。<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默嘅人，但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n錯，應該係100倍先啱<br />\n<br />\n估唔到我喺呢個post竟然見識到你嘅威力<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑到爆咗肚，依家一路打字一路執返啲腸呀內臟呀腎呀，塞返落個肚度。<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過未來幾個月去紅館開棟篤笑？"},{"pid":"7df2f22c2841d0937807747d7bc3fc4c0b9aa458","tid":2208101,"uid":35271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:29:43.000Z","msg":"如果啲光都跨欄咁點"},{"pid":"d058c34db9bb5967a6b212541118a5f370287988","tid":2208101,"uid":6140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:30:02.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"d4c6f57d1527c285ea80babd7143547e46fcabbf